ar for disse oppr\u00f8rende, veldokumenterte og gjentatte bruddene p\u00e5 folkeretten, sier Jonathan Pedneault fra Human Rights Watch.", "(\u00a9NTB)"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|utenriks"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "cb899fd681152f99ca95f2bc0ec02bd111e5c145b8b1d305c37c3f8c998ce583"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-03-31T22:31:54.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Flere tusen hus er brent ned til grunnen og hele landsbyer er forlatt som f\u00f8lge av sikkerhetsstyrkenes herjinger i S\u00f8r-Sudan, konkluderer FN-granskere."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://static.polarismedia.no/skins/prod/publication/adressa/gfx/applefavicon.png"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "256x256"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/6583bde4a1fcbc72c6fa93406d6ca5d73059b2ca.jpg?58df0d3d"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "256x256"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Tusenvis av boliger stukket i brann i S\u00f8r-Sudan -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "6583bde4a1fcbc72c6fa93406d6ca5d73059b2ca"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "utenriks"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "law-government-and-politics"}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": "amnesty international"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["brent", "rapport", "landsby", "oppr\u00f8rere", "boliger stukket", "landet"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["human rights watch", "salva kiir"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["s\u00f8r-sudan", "juba", "yei", "uganda"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "jonathan pedneault"}, {"field": "kw-sentiment", "value": "negati